    {
      "heading": "Durable Construction",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Intercom Sunshield is a vital accessory designed specifically for the UniFi Access Intercom. This weatherproof shield safeguards your intercom from the damaging effects of sunlight and UV radiation, ensuring optimal performance and longevity, even in harsh outdoor environments. Constructed from powder-coated galvanized steel, the shield effectively deflects sunlight and UV rays, safeguarding the delicate internal components of your UniFi Access Intercom. This not only extends the lifespan of your device but also ensures consistent performance throughout its years of service."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Simple Installation",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Intercom Sunshield is designed for effortless installation. It seamlessly integrates with your existing UniFi Access Intercom, requiring no complex modifications or additional tools. The shield attaches securely without interfering with the intercom's functionality, ensuring clear audio and video quality during communication. This user-friendly design allows you to quickly add an extra layer of protection to your intercom system, ensuring its continued performance and reliability in any outdoor environment."
    }
